    "Conway stepped down as co-CEO in January 2018 and now serves as co-executive chairman with cofounder and billionaire David Rubenstein.",
    "The trio took Carlyle public on the Nasdaq exchange in 2012, and the firm now has about $222 billion in assets under management.",
    "They used their Beltway connections--George H.W. Bush was among their advisers--to invest in defense-oriented companies.",
